001package com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.response.historyLog;
002
003import org.apache.commons.lang3.Validate;
004import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.annotations.HistoryLogProps;
005import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.helpers.Bytes;
006
007import java.util.Set;
008
009@HistoryLogProps(
010    opCode = 64,
011    displayName = "Bolus Requested 1/3",
012    internalName = "LID_BOLUS_REQUESTED_MSG1",
013    usedByAndroid = true,
014    usedByTidepool = true
015)
016public class BolusRequestedMsg1HistoryLog extends HistoryLog {
017    
018    private int bolusId;
019    private int bolusTypeId;
020    private boolean correctionBolusIncluded;
021    private int carbAmount;
022    private int bg;
023    private float iob;
024    private long carbRatio;
025    
026    public BolusRequestedMsg1HistoryLog() {}
027    
028    public BolusRequestedMsg1HistoryLog(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, int bolusId, int bolusTypeId, boolean correctionBolusIncluded, int carbAmount, int bg, float iob, long carbRatio) {
029        super(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum);
030        this.cargo = buildCargo(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum, bolusId, bolusTypeId, correctionBolusIncluded, carbAmount, bg, iob, carbRatio);
031        this.bolusId = bolusId;
032        this.bolusTypeId = bolusTypeId; // probably the same bolusType enum as BolusDeliveryHistoryLog
033        this.correctionBolusIncluded = correctionBolusIncluded;
034        this.carbAmount = carbAmount;
035        this.bg = bg;
036        this.iob = iob;
037        this.carbRatio = carbRatio;
038        
039    }
040
041    public int typeId() {
042        return 64;
043    }
044
045    /**
046     * <table border="1">
047     * <caption>Parsed fields for BolusRequestedMsg1HistoryLog:</caption>
048     * <tr><td><code>bolusId</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 10)</code></td></tr>
049     * <tr><td><code>bolusTypeId</code></td><td><code>raw[12]</code></td></tr>
050     * <tr><td><code>correctionBolusIncluded</code></td><td><code>raw[13] != 0</code></td></tr>
051     * <tr><td><code>carbAmount</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 14)</code></td></tr>
052     * <tr><td><code>bg</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 16)</code></td></tr>
053     * <tr><td><code>iob</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readFloat(raw, 18)</code></td></tr>
054     * <tr><td><code>carbRatio</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readUint32(raw, 22)</code></td></tr>
055     * </table>
056     */
057    public void parse(byte[] raw) {
058        Validate.isTrue(raw.length == 26);
059        this.cargo = raw;
060        parseBase(raw);
061        this.bolusId = Bytes.readShort(raw, 10);
062        this.bolusTypeId = raw[12];
063        this.correctionBolusIncluded = raw[13] != 0;
064        this.carbAmount = Bytes.readShort(raw, 14);
065        this.bg = Bytes.readShort(raw, 16);
066        this.iob = Bytes.readFloat(raw, 18);
067        this.carbRatio = Bytes.readUint32(raw, 22);
068        
069    }
070
071    
072    /**
073     * <table border="1">
074     * <caption>Byte layout for BolusRequestedMsg1HistoryLog.buildCargo(...):</caption>
075     * <tr><th>Offset</th><th>Description</th></tr>
076     * <tr><td>0</td><td><code>new byte[]{64} [element 0]</code></td></tr>
077     * <tr><td>1</td><td><code>new byte[]{0} [element 1]</code></td></tr>
078     * <tr><td>2</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
079     * <tr><td>3</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
080     * <tr><td>4</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
081     * <tr><td>5</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
082     * <tr><td>6</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
083     * <tr><td>7</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
084     * <tr><td>8</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
085     * <tr><td>9</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
086     * <tr><td>10</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(bolusId) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
087     * <tr><td>11</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(bolusId) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
088     * <tr><td>12</td><td><code>(byte) bolusType</code></td></tr>
089     * <tr><td>13</td><td><code>(byte) (correctionBolusIncluded ? 1 : 0)</code></td></tr>
090     * <tr><td>14</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(carbAmount) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
091     * <tr><td>15</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(carbAmount) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
092     * <tr><td>16</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(bg) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
093     * <tr><td>17</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(bg) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
094     * <tr><td>18</td><td><code>toFloat(iob) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
095     * <tr><td>19</td><td><code>toFloat(iob) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
096     * <tr><td>20</td><td><code>toFloat(iob) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
097     * <tr><td>21</td><td><code>toFloat(iob) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
098     * <tr><td>22</td><td><code>toUint32(carbRatio) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
099     * <tr><td>23</td><td><code>toUint32(carbRatio) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
100     * <tr><td>24</td><td><code>toUint32(carbRatio) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
101     * <tr><td>25</td><td><code>toUint32(carbRatio) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
102     * </table>
103     */
104    public static byte[] buildCargo(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, int bolusId, int bolusType, boolean correctionBolusIncluded, int carbAmount, int bg, float iob, long carbRatio) {
105        return Bytes.combine(
106            new byte[]{64, 0},
107            Bytes.toUint32(pumpTimeSec),
108            Bytes.toUint32(sequenceNum),
109            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(bolusId), 
110            new byte[]{ (byte) bolusType }, 
111            new byte[]{ (byte) (correctionBolusIncluded ? 1 : 0) }, 
112            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(carbAmount), 
113            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(bg), 
114            Bytes.toFloat(iob), 
115            Bytes.toUint32(carbRatio));
116    }
117
118    /**
119     * @return the ID of the bolus operation
120     */
121    public int getBolusId() {
122        return bolusId;
123    }
124
125    public int getBolusTypeId() {
126        return bolusTypeId;
127    }
128
129    /**
130     * @return Bolus types
131     */
132    public Set<BolusDeliveryHistoryLog.BolusType> getBolusType() {
133        return BolusDeliveryHistoryLog.BolusType.fromBitmask(bolusTypeId);
134    }
135
136    /**
137     * @return if the correction bolus is included
138     */
139    public boolean getCorrectionBolusIncluded() {
140        return correctionBolusIncluded;
141    }
142
143    /**
144     * @return carbs in grams
145     */
146    public int getCarbAmount() {
147        return carbAmount;
148    }
149
150    /**

152     */
153    public int getBg() {
154        return bg;
155    }
156
157    /**
158     * @return current insulin on board
159     */
160    public float getIob() {
161        return iob;
162    }
163
164    /**
165     * @return carb ratio from the insulin delivery profile
166     */
167    public long getCarbRatio() {
168        return carbRatio;
169    }
